ranking.readme_summary: Grok-1 This repository contains JAX example code for loading and running the Grok-1 open-weights model. Make sure to download the checkpoint and place the ckpt-0 directory in checkpoints - see Downloading the weights Then, run to test the code. The script loads the checkpoint and samples from the model on a test input
